    rdfs:label "Design System (shadcn-svelte)" ;
    pred:description "shadcn-svelte foundation on Tailwind v4, themed to the Liquid aesthetic. Preflight (Tailwind's CSS reset) is deliberately omitted — src/lib/styles/tailwind.css imports only the theme and utilities layers, so global.css remains the visual source of truth and the app renders unchanged. Every shadcn token is a var() reference into global.css (e.g. --color-primary -> --accent teal); shadcn's neutral 'accent' hover slot is kept inside @theme only, never clobbering the Liquid --accent custom property. Starter components: button, badge, card, separator, skeleton under src/lib/components/ui/. Pilot: the About-footer 'Send feedback' button." ;
